{@link addressConfig} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
Configuration for account address button
It's an optional parameter.

{@link appearance} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
Sets style for appearance.
You can use one of the values from enum {@link AUC_BALANCE_APPEARANCE}.
It's an optional parameter.

{@link color} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
Sets theme of the button.
It's an optional parameter. The default value is white.
You can use enum {@link AS_COLOR_GROUP}. If selected appearance transparent, color is ignored.
{@link identicon} - Shows identicon if provided.

{@link isCurrency} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
Shows Currency icon from supported networks list.
You will set supported networks when initialize library, {@link AucNetworkOption.icon}.
It's an optional parameter. The default value is false.

{@link onAddressClick} - It's an `@Output()` parameter.
Emits an action when account button was clicked.
Emitted value is native click value.

{@link showAddress} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
Show or hide account address.
It's an optional parameter. The default value is false.

{@link account} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
User account related information.
Required parameter.

{@link optionEmitter} - It's an `@Output()` parameter.
Emits selected option from the list.

{@link options} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
List of options in popover.
It's an optional parameter.

{@link size} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
Sets size of the avatar.
It's an optional parameter. The default value is 40.

{@link color} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
Theme color palette for the alert. This sets the alert background color.
It's an optional parameter. The default value is red.

{@link icon}  It's an `Input()` parameter.
This sets the alert icon otherwise itll be hidden.
You can use supported icons from enum {@link AUC_WLC_ICON} or string.
If you want to use custom icon you need to provide url to the image as a string value.
It's an optional parameter.
This is required parameter.

{@link iconPosition} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
Controls icon position.
It's an optional parameter. The default value is right.
You can use enum {@link AUC_ALERT_POSITION}

{@link text} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
The message to show in the alert.
This is required parameter.

{@link size} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
Sets size of the avatar.
It's an optional parameter. The default value is 40.

{@link src} - It's an `@Input()` parameter.
Sets provided image url as avatar otherwise default user icon will be shown.
It's an optional parameter.
Used for lock / unlock scroll for body.

tags.text:
lockScroll add class `block-scroll` to body;
This class will block scroll for body;

unlockScroll remove class `block-scroll` from body;
This class will unlock scroll for body;
